                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0Bx4BSt6jniD7dlN4cEMwWm9Tc28/layout_metrics_touchtarget3.png",
                      "caption": "<p>Touch target height: 48dp <br>Button height: 36dp</p>"
                    },
